Package biolockj.module.implicit.parser.r16s

This package contains Parser BioModules that convert the 16S taxonomy reports generated by 16S classifiers (such as RDP and QIIME) into standardized OTU abundance tables.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    QiimeParser
    This BioModules parses QiimeClassifier output reports to build standard OTU abundance tables.
    RdpParser
    This BioModule parses RDP output files to build standard OTU abundance tables.
